Root Cause & Issue Summary
What Went Wrong
During a weekend deployment, a bug caused duplicate reference numbers to be generated for Option Assignment/Exercise trades (E-Trade accounts). Because of these duplicate reference numbers, when trades went through the back-bridging process, they were kicked out and never passed to Margin — flagged as duplicates in the PNS kick-out report.

Impact
