What Will NOT Be Recovered

Fields already published to EDW and T++ via the distributed activity file — those will not be republished, meaning certain legacy mainframe attributes will remain missing permanently for these trades.


Resolution Plan

Manually recreate the 2,400 trades into the mainframe file and republish via end-of-day batch
Identify the missing fields backbridged from mainframe to distributed activity and communicate impact to downstream consumers
Reverse the $84M plug once trades are replayed
Update ICO with the full list of 2,400 affected trades
